==English==

===Etymology===
See etymology under '''[[perspicacious]]'''.

===Pronunciation===
Syllables: per·spi·cac·i·ty<br>
[[AHD]]: pûrʹspĭ·kăsʹə·tē<br>
[[IPA]]: /ˌpɜːr.spɪˈkæs.ə.tiː/

===Noun===
'''perspicacity'''

# The power to see or understand clearly; sharp-sightedness; insight.
# Acute ability to discern, understand, or assess.

